3. zod
   Licensed under MIT.
   Runtime schema validation for tool arguments.

4. dotenv
   Licensed under BSD-2-Clause.
   Loads environment configuration.

5. snarkjs
   Licensed under GPL-3.0.
   Groth16 proof generation for the ZK shuffle / decrypt prover tools
