================================================================================
ZK trusted setup
================================================================================

The ZK prover tools consume verifying-key / proving-key (.zkey) artifacts and
circuit build outputs produced in the main AgenticZK repository. The current
artifacts come from a single-party Powers of Tau ceremony intended for
development and testnet use ONLY. They are NOT safe for mainnet or any high-value
deployment until replaced by the output of a public multi-party (>=10 participant)
ceremony. See the main repo's docs/CEREMONY_OUTREACH.md for ceremony status.
